1311:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Configure simple output channel
1312:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple output compare
1313:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple output compare
1314:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple output compare and enable interrupt
1315:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple output compare and disable interrupt
1316:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple output compare and enable DMA transfer
1317:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple output compare and disable DMA transfer
1318:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****        -@- When a HRTIM timer operates in simple output compare mode
1319:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****            the output level is set to a programmable value when a match
1320:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****            is found between the compare register and the counter.
1321:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****            Compare unit 1 is automatically associated to output 1
1322:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****            Compare unit 2 is automatically associated to output 2
1323:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c **** @endverbatim
