1925:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****               ##### Simple PWM output functions #####
1926:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  ===============================================================================
1927:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****     [..]  This section provides functions allowing to:
1928:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Configure simple PWM output channel
1929:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple PWM output
1930:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple PWM output
1931:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple PWM output and enable interrupt
1932:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple PWM output and disable interrupt
1933:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple PWM output and enable DMA transfer
1934:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple PWM output and disable DMA transfer
1935:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       -@- When a HRTIM timer operates in simple PWM output mode
1936:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           the output level is set to a programmable value when a match is
1937:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           found between the compare register and the counter and reset when
1938:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           the timer period is reached. Duty cycle is determined by the
1939:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           comparison value.
1940:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           Compare unit 1 is automatically associated to output 1
1941:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           Compare unit 2 is automatically associated to output 2
1942:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c **** @endverbatim
