2606:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****               ##### Simple input capture functions #####
2607:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  ===============================================================================
2608:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****     [..]  This section provides functions allowing to:
2609:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Configure simple input capture channel
2610:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple input capture
2611:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple input capture
2612:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple input capture and enable interrupt
2613:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple input capture and disable interrupt
2614:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Start simple input capture and enable DMA transfer
2615:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       (+) Stop simple input capture and disable DMA transfer
2616:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****       -@- When a HRTIM timer operates in simple input capture mode
2617:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****           the Capture Register (HRTIM_CPT1/2xR) is used to latch the
2618:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****          value of the timer counter counter after a transition detected
2619:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****          on a given external event input.
2620:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c **** @endverbatim
