6524:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Output 1 and output 2 reset (transition active to inactive)
6525:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Output 1 and output 2 set (transition inactive to active)
