6527:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Timing unit registers update
6528:Drivers/STM32F3xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f3xx_hal_hrtim.c ****  *            - Repetition event
